      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" id="what-makes-a-great-ielts-prep-course">What Makes a Great IELTS Prep Course?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">IELTS preparation is different from general English study. You need a course that addresses all four modules: Listening, Reading, Writing, and Speaking. The best IELTS prep courses combine structured learning with practical exam strategies and regular feedback from qualified instructors.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">When choosing an IELTS prep course, look for these non-negotiable features:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 mb-6">
        <li>Coverage of both IELTS Academic and General Training formats</li>
        <li>Official IELTS practice materials and authentic test simulations</li>
        <li>Instructor feedback on speaking and writing tasks</li>
        <li>Band score tracking so you can measure your progress</li>
        <li>Flexible scheduling to fit around your work or study commitments</li>
        <li>Strategies specific to each question type in every module</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" id="8-top-rated-ielts-prep-courses-for-2026">8 Top-Rated IELTS Prep Courses for 2026</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">We tested and reviewed the most popular IELTS preparation options available. Here are the eight that stood out for their quality, value, and proven results.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">1. iTalki IELTS</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">From $8 per session</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">1-on-1 tutoring with certified IELTS teachers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="text-sm text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Review</a>
            <a href="/go/italki" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Visit iTalki
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-3 leading-relaxed">iTalki connects you with both community tutors and professional IELTS teachers for personalised 1-on-1 sessions. You can filter specifically for tutors who specialize in IELTS modules, book trial lessons at reduced rates, and build a study plan that targets your weak areas. Sessions start from $8, making it one of the most affordable ways to get expert IELTS coaching.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">What sets iTalki apart is the sheer variety of tutors available. Whether you need intensive Writing Task 2 practice, speaking confidence building, or full mock test feedback, you can find a tutor who matches your specific needs and schedule.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">2. See Guru</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">From $12 per session</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">AI-matched IELTS tutors with progress tracking</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a href="/reviews/see-guru/" class="text-sm text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Review</a>
            <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Try See Guru
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3">We earn a commission from qualifying purchases made through this link, at no extra cost to you.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">See Guru uses AI to match you with IELTS tutors based on your current band level and target score. The platform provides structured lesson plans, mock tests, and regular progress reports. See Guru is particularly strong for learners who want a guided journey from their starting band to their target, with consistent tutor support throughout.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3. E2 Language</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">From $30/month</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Video courses with IELTS expert teachers</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/go/e2language" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Visit E2 Language
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">E2 Language is run by former IELTS examiners who break down exactly what examiners look for in each module. Their video courses cover every question type with worked examples, and their writing correction service gives you detailed feedback from certified IELTS teachers. E2 Language is ideal for self-motivated learners who want examiner-grade instruction at an accessible price.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">4. Preply IELTS</h3>
