              Visit Preply
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Preply carefully vets its IELTS tutors and allows you to filter by experience, student ratings, and specific module expertise. Every tutor on the platform is reviewed by Preply before they can teach. The platform offers a free trial session so you can assess chemistry and teaching style before committing. Preply is excellent for learners who value quality assurance and want to choose from a curated selection of tutors.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">5. British Council IELTS Prep</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">Free to paid options</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Official IELTS materials from the test creators</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/go/british-council" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Visit British Council
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">The British Council offers free IELTS preparation resources including practice tests, videos, and skills-building materials. Their paid IELTS Prep course provides a structured 4-week program with live classes, writing feedback, and mock tests marked by certified teachers. As the co-creator of the IELTS test, the British Council has unmatched access to official materials and examiner insight.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">6. IELTS Liz</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">Free and paid tiers</p>
