            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">IELTS Liz is run by a veteran IELTS teacher who has helped hundreds of thousands of learners prepare for the test. Her YouTube-style video lessons cover every module in detail, with free videos on YouTube and a paid membership offering additional practice tests, model answers, and live tutoring sessions. IELTS Liz is especially popular among self-study learners who want high-quality instruction without the cost of a full course.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">7. Magoosh IELTS</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">From $99/month</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Self-paced video lessons with email tutor support</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/go/magoosh" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Visit Magoosh
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Magoosh offers a comprehensive self-paced IELTS preparation course with over 250 video lessons, hundreds of practice questions, and email access to IELTS tutors for personalised support. The platform is best suited for disciplined learners who prefer studying independently but want the security of tutor access when questions arise. Magoosh guarantees a 0.5 band score improvement for students who complete the required study plan.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">8. Cambly IELTS</h3>
      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700">From $15/month</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Unlimited speaking practice with native speakers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a href="/reviews/cambly/" class="text-sm text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Review</a>
            <a href="/go/cambly" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
              Visit Cambly
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Cambly is not exclusively an IELTS platform, but its IELTS-specific curriculum provides unlimited conversation practice with native English speakers. This is particularly valuable for the speaking module, where comfort with native pronunciation and natural responses directly impacts your band score. Cambly is best used alongside a structured IELTS course to complement self-study with live speaking practice.</p>

      <AdUnit />

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" id="ielts-prep-course-comparison">IELTS Prep Course Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
