      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" id="how-to-choose-the-right-ielts-prep-course">How to Choose the Right IELTS Prep Course</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Your ideal IELTS prep course depends on three factors: your current band level, your target band score, and your available budget. Here is a quick decision guide:</p>

      <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
