            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold mt-0.5">Band 5.5 to 6.5:</span>
            <span>E2 Language or British Council IELTS Prep are ideal for structured learning with examiner insight.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold mt-0.5">Band 6.5 to 7.5:</span>
            <span>Preply or iTalki with a certified IELTS professional coach for targeted feedback on your weak modules.</span>
