            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold mt-0.5">Band 7.5+ target:</span>
            <span>Combine Magoosh self-study with frequent 1-on-1 sessions on See Guru or iTalki for polishing every module.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

